data.description: Check out this move-in ready 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom home located in a cul-de-sac on almost 1/2 an acre. Home has been very well maintained with updates throughout! No carpet with wet protect/pet protect laminate flooring installed in 2021 throughout and tile in the bathrooms. Kitchen features eat-in area, new island, new refrigerator and new garbage disposal. Large living room is the perfect place to relax next to the fireplace with new insert and propane tank. Back porch off of the living room was finished in by licensed contractor, creating a nice flex space to use as you'd like. Master bedroom is huge with large walk-in closet. Bonus room upstairs has a newly added closet. New roof with 30 year shingles was installed in 2022. Home has a huge backyard with pressure treated privacy fence with recently planted crepe myrtles and Oktoberfest maple trees.
